'''Himetric''' is a [[metric system|metric]] measurement of length similar to [[twip]]s, used in computing. It is one thousandth of a centimeter (i.e. 10&nbsp;[[µm]]) and is [[Resolution independence|independent of]] the [[display resolution|display or screen resolution]].
